{"tid":1778110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【東錦賽】回應「殺人功夫攔截」 姜至鵬：他的頭碰到我的腳","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T01:08:36.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9f21cf48d81dd3d921bbf0e73db621d7fbdb12","tid":1778110,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:29:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191210/AEPNLOPRAYDBQHZMJ2ICESIVDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191210%2FAEPNLOPRAYDBQHZMJ2ICESIVDM%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=96afef44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191210%2FAEPNLOPRAYDBQHZMJ2ICESIVDM%2F&h=7c501977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191210/AEPNLOPRAYDBQHZMJ2ICESIVDM/</a><br />\n中國男足周二在東亞足球錦標賽首戰，以1:2不敵日本，當中姜至鵬一次「裂頭腳式」粗野攔截成為全場焦點，該名30歲左閘賽後強調無意傷人，又指球證未有以紅牌將他驅逐出場的做法正確。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上半場30分鐘，姜至鵬在攔截皮球時，跳起並將左腳高高舉起，結果踢中日本守將橋岡大樹的頭部，但球證只向他出示黃牌警告。<br />\n<br />\n有日本傳媒以「殺人功夫攔截」來形容姜至鵬的犯規動作，但他強調自己無心傷人：「我沒有故意傷害任何人，我覺得他不可能頂到球，大家可以看重播，是我的腳先截下球，隨後他的頭碰到我。」<br />\n<br />\n姜至鵬又說：「那個球我沒有蹬踹的動作，所以給紅牌還是不大可能。」"},{"pid":"b87a7d5c2a7a39de21521e005c5f6693f00bf958","tid":1778110,"uid":44718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母, 鞋面踩你鞋底啲Friend?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacae9738ae6a44fc572f5d0568a6c354633aa47","tid":1778110,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6f1826c0c596021b4ae4d2ecc52ae68540bf82","tid":1778110,"uid":340794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"證明香港警察被染紅，行為舉止言語都一模一樣，可以早日成為黨的太保"},{"pid":"95f4e21652a636a5fc6602866fcd37d5e6e5c38c","tid":177811